channel.title: [Delta]Looking for a co-developer
channel.description:
I've been working on a delta server and its just about done to be publish and have a beta opening in december, but I would like a partner since being the only coder it will be pretty hard to fell players needs and wants.
I'm looking for both a coder on the server and one for the client. If you can do both that will be great!
Application [code]Age: Position applying for: Past work: Experience: Dedication to a project (on a scale of 1 to 10): Skype/Any type of contact info:[/code]
For the experience it would be great if you could show something, but its not necessary. For the Skype/Any type of contact info..don't give me your legit address or phone number for the any type of contact info it can be email or a texting app that you will check.
Heres what the server looks like so far... [url=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,633801.msg4280442.html#msg4280442]http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,633801.msg4280442.html#msg4280442[/url]
